Hi Johnny, I think the open sky looks much better, it would allow me to play with the lighting a bit more and the additional floor makes it feel like a more open space.
I'm glad the scale is looking correct. I'll begin working on this, but before I begin would you have any tips on creating correct floor/ceiling tile size?
